{"tid":488991,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真求意見］雙學士其實有無用","createTime":"2017-12-04T08:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T06:34:47.000Z","uid":161548,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"886583c5637c6e88137277bd2ab1704740454c71","tid":488991,"uid":161548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T08:59:28.000Z","msg":"我認自己讀書唔算太好<br />\nDSE完左入CIE 呢家讀緊top up第一個sem<br />\n但前排已經決定左會去外國讀多個degree<br />\n唔讀master因為我驚handle唔到 始終新環境同能力有限<br />\n呢家諗緊應唔應該quit左佢然後直接出去浸<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得我應該讀埋落去先再出去讀 攞雙學士<br />\n定係慳返年半時間同10萬學費直接出國讀 攞CIE asso同外國大學degree<br />\n希望大家比啲意見細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8ad91e18ec929ffca5ba0f48a76764a7aa516a","tid":488991,"uid":62646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/180216_661e3fc6a0f98653ec0d2ed362deddfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F180216_661e3fc6a0f98653ec0d2ed362deddfa.jpg&h=8b315142&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bc96708680123ad585f845885dd2dd143beba79","tid":488991,"uid":10844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:08:48.000Z","msg":"美國哈哈哈哈佛大學"},{"pid":"2c1c108b1c251d38cbb1705502de079fd4f661e3","tid":488991,"uid":161548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:38:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國哈哈哈哈佛大學</blockquote><br />\n劍劍劍劍橋大學"},{"pid":"f25aa118c19874590289e373081ed1a2b155b21a","tid":488991,"uid":161548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"跪係到求意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76701ad0995d63c08bdcdf227ceb8d81eda5713","tid":488991,"uid":76931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:40:49.000Z","msg":"咩degree唔講點幫你