gmoji\" /> <br />\n呢家諗清楚就想轉<br />\n加拿大澳洲英國嘅話點揀好<br />\nBtw thankyou"},{"pid":"95d7509e3d1e0d05955ebb841598fea8be62bf96","tid":488991,"uid":1424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實入CIE 呢步已經錯左<br />\n除非你諗住第二個degree 既pre req 係要有1st degree，否則你呢個degree 就無用<br />\n<br />\n我係你既我會而家quit cie，一係直接出黎做嘢，一係過英國/澳洲讀foun/美國讀cc<br />\n三個option 入面英國抵d，因為只係四年，而學費比普遍美國便宜<br />\n（on the assumption that 你唔係去london）</blockquote><br />\n我都知唔應該入 果陣年少無知諗住見步行步有得讀就讀嘅心態入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢家諗清楚就想轉<br />\n加拿大澳洲英國嘅話點揀好<br />\nBtw thankyou</blockquote><br />\n我個人會揀英國<br />\n一來degree 讀三年，二來生活費相對便宜"},{"pid":"94b7aea3a51ff635717c729966afa6a06726a511","tid":488991,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:34:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/180216_661e3fc6a0f98653ec0d2ed362deddfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F180216_661e3fc6a0f98653ec0d2ed362deddfa.jpg&h=8b315142&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雙學士喎"}]}